  "title": "Working with Files",
  "content_md": "# File Handling in Python\n\nFiles store data that programs can read and write.\n\n## Read a File\n```python\nwith open('data.txt', 'r') as f:\n    content = f.read()\n```\n\n## Write a File\n```python\nwith open('output.txt', 'w') as f:\n    f.write('Hello!')\n```",
